(43, NULL, 'China ups cash rewards for citizens who report porn', 'China is raising the cash rewards paid to citizens for reporting pornographic and \"illegal\" publications to authorities, government regulators ...', 'https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/china-ups-cash-rewards-for-citizens-report-porn-wechat-wei', 'http://www.channelnewsasia.com/image/10939102/16x9/991/557/971f3b342ea9bd589eb5c364df0ff961/tj/china-s-broad-definition-of--illegal--content-includes-works-that--endanger-national-unity---leak-state-secrets--and--disturb-social-order--1542371849663-2.jpg', '2018-11-16T13:20:02Z', 'BEIJING: China is raising the cash rewards paid to citizens for reporting pornographic and \"illegal\" publications to authorities, government regulators said Friday (Nov 16). Starting Dec 1, people can rake in up to 600,000 yuan (US$86,000) for reporting illeg… [+1591 chars]', '2018/11/16 03:34:35pm', 'top-headlines'),
(44, 'Vivian Ho', 'California firefighter: hot, sweaty, tough … and the best job in the world', 'For those battling the deadly wildfires ravaging the state, shifts can be 48 hours of backbreaking work in daunting conditions', 'https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/nov/16/california-firefighter-hot-sweaty-tough-and-the-best', 'https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/1eee84962029128e592fdd9265e7ce116d0d3086/0_192_5760_3456/master/5760.jpg?width=1200&height=630&quality=85&auto=format&fit=crop&overlay-align=bottom%2Cleft&overlay-width=100p&overlay-base64=L2ltZy9zdGF0aWMvb3ZlcmxheXMvdGctZGVmYXVsdC5wbmc&s=73039f476935280dce090e135992c9d8', '2018-11-16T12:55:00Z', 'S teep, 12-mile hikes up rocky, arduous terrains with 50 pounds of gear on your back. Endless, sometimes 48-hour-long shifts of backbreaking work, cutting and clearing away vegetation. No showers for days as the sweat soaks through and hardens your fire-resis… [+6082 chars]', '2018/11/16 03:34:35pm', 'top-headlines'),
(45, NULL, 'Zimbabwe bus fire: More than 40 people feared killed, 24 injured', 'Scores of people are believed dead and more than 20 have been taken to hospital with injuries after a suspected gas tank leak sparks a fire.', 'https://www.abc.net.au/news/2018-11-16/zimbabwe-bus-fire-feared-killed-more-than-40/10506906', 'https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/10506924-16x9-700x394.jpg', '2018-11-16T12:36:55Z', 'Posted November 16, 2018 23:36:55 At least 42 people are feared dead after a bus caught fire in Zimbabwe, with police forced to pull the charred remains of passengers from the vehicle\'s shell. The Red Cross said the accident was \"horrific\" It said the bodies … [+1090 chars]', '2018/11/16 03:34:35pm', 'top-headlines'),
(46, 'Josh Noble, Chelsea Bruce-Lockhart, Monika Pronczu', 'Brexit deal crisis: Gove to stay on – live', 'A live blog from FT.com', 'https://www.ft.com/content/af877acd-c943-3ea4-ab77-4251830baa02', 'https://www.ft.com/__origami/service/image/v2/images/raw/http%3A%2F%2Fblogs.ft.com%2Fwestminster%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F11%2FMAS_UKNews__3D4FD552E5FE4D09-B04AA3F452E57909_20181116102149.jpg?source=next-opengraph&fit=scale-down&width=900', '2018-11-16T12:34:00Z', 'If parliament rejects, what next? If parliament rejects the Brexit deal agreed between the UK and the EU, think-tank the Centre for European Reform has some ideas about what could come next. A CER report outlines five possible options: no deal, renegotiation … [+1117 chars]', '2018/11/16 03:34:35pm', 'top-headlines'),
(47, NULL, 'North Korean leader Kim Jong-un has visited test site of new weapon, state media says', 'With negotiations between Pyongyang and Washington appearing to have stalled, state media reports the North Korean leader has visited the test site of a new tactical weapon.', 'https://www.abc.net.au/news/2018-11-16/north-korean-leader-kim-jong-un-visits-missile-site/10506674', 'https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/10506712-16x9-700x394.jpg', '2018-11-16T12:12:57Z', 'Updated November 16, 2018 23:26:37 North Korean leader Kim Jong-un has visited the test site of a new tactical weapon in his first public \"field inspection\" since last year, hailing it as a \"display of our rapidly-growing defence capabilities\", according to s… [+4487 chars]', '2018/11/16 03:34:35pm', 'top-headlines'),
