(52, 'Fikayo Olowolagba', '2019: INEC announces date for commencement of presidential, NASS election campaign', 'The Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) will on Sunday lift the ban on campaign for the 2019 presidential and National Assembly elections slat', 'http://dailypost.ng/2018/11/17/2019-inec-announces-date-commencement-presidential-nass-election-camp', 'http://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/INEC-3.png', '2018-11-17T15:59:03Z', 'The Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) will on Sunday lift the ban on campaign for the 2019 presidential and National Assembly elections slated for February 16, 2019 A statement by Mr Oluwole Osaze-Uzzi, INEC’s Director of Voter Education and Pu… [+834 chars]', '2018/11/17 05:46:52pm', 'top-headlines'),
(53, 'Martin Chulov', 'CIA Khashoggi findings \'highly damaging\' to Mohammed bin Salman', 'Agency must have solid proof that de facto leader ordered journalist’s killing, says official', 'https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/nov/17/cia-khashoggi-findings-highly-damaging-to-saudi-prince', 'https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/0f9b5e3b94a2cef6d8abb87503745163d70228a8/0_190_2462_1477/master/2462.jpg?width=1200&height=630&quality=85&auto=format&fit=crop&overlay-align=bottom%2Cleft&overlay-width=100p&overlay-base64=L2ltZy9zdGF0aWMvb3ZlcmxheXMvdGctZGVmYXVsdC5wbmc&s=7b0aab0b65cf8248eda9fe8f85a16a2c', '2018-11-17T15:55:38Z', 'The CIA’s conclusion that the murder of Jamal Khashoggi was ordered by Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman has been described as the most damaging blow yet to the de facto Saudi leader, officially placing him at the heart of a scandal that continues to shake the… [+5034 chars]', '2018/11/17 05:46:52pm', 'top-headlines'),
(54, 'Don Silas', 'South Africa vs Nigeria: Rohr reveals why Super Eagles played 1-1 with Bafana Bafana', 'Super Eagles technical adviser, Gernot Rohr has explained why his side played a 1-1 draw with South Africa in Saturday’s 2019 Africa Cup of Nations, AFCON,', 'http://dailypost.ng/2018/11/17/south-africa-vs-nigeria-rohr-reveals-super-eagles-played-1-1-bafana-b', 'http://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/6581A56F-E190-4330-8209-720C6E4E9AC5.jpeg', '2018-11-17T15:53:46Z', 'Super Eagles technical adviser, Gernot Rohr has explained why his side played a 1-1 draw with South Africa in Saturday’s 2019 Africa Cup of Nations, AFCON, qualifying fixture at the BFN Stadium in Johannesburg. An own goal from South Africa defender, Buhle Mk… [+819 chars]', '2018/11/17 05:46:52pm', 'top-headlines'),
