(100, NULL, 'N540b recovered through whistle blower policy, says minister - The Nation Newspaper', 'MINISTER of Information and Culture Lai Mohammed said yesterday that the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission (EFFC) has so far recovered', 'http://thenationonlineng.net/n540b-recovered-whistle-blower-policy-says-minister/', 'http://thenationonlineng.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/863c027e-lai.jpg', '2018-11-27T23:02:51Z', 'MINISTER of Information and Culture Lai Mohammed said yesterday that the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission (EFFC) has so far recovered over N540 billion through the Whistle Blower Policy. He stated this yesterday at the 71st General Assembly of the Bro… [+3067 chars]', '2018/11/28 10:47:22am', 'top-headlines'),
(101, 'Eurosport UK', 'Football news - WATCH: David De Gea produces sensational \'save of the year\' - Eurosport.com', 'FACT: David De Gea is good at goalkeeping.', 'https://www.eurosport.com/football/champions-league/2018-2019/football-news-watch-david-de-gea-produ', 'https://i.eurosport.com/2018/11/27/2470717-51313057-1600-900.jpg', '2018-11-27T21:52:47Z', 'The Manchester United man has done it again. De Gea pulled off a sensational save to keep the scores level as United hosted Young Boys on Tuesday evening. If you don\'t believe this lot then feel free to watch it for yourself below... Absolutely brilliant! Obv… [+148 chars]', '2018/11/28 10:47:22am', 'top-headlines'),
(102, 'siteadmin', 'Ladoja: Adedibu Plotted My Impeachment Because I Refused To Give Him Oyo\'s Security Votes - SaharaReporters.com', '“The group that called for my impeachment was led by the late Alhaji Lamidi Adedibu. The politician believed he had a right to security votes because he was securing the state but I thought otherwise,\" Ladoja said.', 'http://saharareporters.com/2018/11/27/ladoja-adedibu-plotted-my-impeachment-because-i-refused-give-h', NULL, '2018-11-27T20:00:53Z', 'The 11-year-old trial of a former Governor of Oyo State, Chief Rashidi Ladoja, for alleged N4.7bn fraud came to a close on Tuesday after the ex-governor testified in his own defence before the Federal High Court in Lagos. The Economic and Financial Crimes Com… [+2760 chars]', '2018/11/28 10:47:22am', 'top-headlines'),
(103, 'Fikayo Olowolagba', 'Explain to Nigerians how 44 soldiers were killed in Metele - Bishop Okonkwo tells Buhari - Daily Post Nigeria', 'Ex-president of the Pentecostal Fellowship of Nigeria (PFN) and General Overseer of The Redeemed Evangelical Mission (TREM), Bishop Mike Okonkwo, has calle', 'http://dailypost.ng/2018/11/27/explain-nigerians-44-soldiers-killed-metele-bishop-okonkwo-tells-buha', 'http://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Bishop-Mike-Okonkwo.jpg', '2018-11-27T19:52:30Z', 'Ex-president of the Pentecostal Fellowship of Nigeria (PFN) and General Overseer of The Redeemed Evangelical Mission (TREM), Bishop Mike Okonkwo, has called on the Federal Government to explain to Nigerians what really led to the death of 44 soldiers in Metel… [+1292 chars]', '2018/11/28 10:47:22am', 'top-headlines'),
(104, 'Partner', 'Facebook hosts TechCrunch Startup Battlefield Africa 2018 in Lagos - TechCabal', 'On the 11th of December, the TechCrunch Startup Battlefield takes place. Here, startups in Africa will pitch to a live audience of 500 people ranging from VCs, investors, Government officials, developers and startups', 'https://techcabal.com/2018/12/10/facebook-hosts-techcrunch-startup-battlefield-africa-2018-in-lagos/', 'https://techcabal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/techcrunch-battlefield-africa-2018-competition.png', '2018-12-10T18:31:30Z', 'TechCrunch Startup Battlefield Africa 2018 is here! And guess what? Its being sponsored by Facebook in Lagos, Nigeria. What is the TechCrunch event about? Simple. The TechCrunch Startup Battlefield Africa is a platform that celebrates African founders and ent… [+1871 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines');
