(105, 'siteadmin', '\'It\'s Fake News By PDP\' — Garba Shehu Denies Atiku\'s Son\'s House Was Raided - SaharaReporters.com', '\"Nigerians must be becoming wary by now, of a political party with absolutely nothing to offer in the coming elections and has instead, transformed into a knight in shining armor, slaying the truth. In this so-called transformation, PDP has changed i', 'http://saharareporters.com/2018/12/10/its-fake-news-pdp-%E2%80%94-garba-shehu-denies-atikus-sons-hou', NULL, '2018-12-10T18:16:07Z', 'Garba Shehu, Senior Special Assistant to the President (Media and Publicity), has said the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) is a \"flowing stream of fake news\". He stated this in response to the reports that the account of the PDP vice-presidential candidate was… [+1148 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(106, 'View all posts by Tony ?', 'StarTimes drums support for people living with HIV/AIDS - Vanguard', 'As part of activities to mark the 2018 World AIDS Day, pay-TV company, StarTimes have called for more support to be given to Nigerians living with the virus across the country.', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/2018/12/startimes-drums-support-for-people-living-with-hiv-aids/', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/star-hiv.jpg', '2018-12-10T18:04:47Z', 'As part of activities to mark the 2018 World AIDS Day, pay-TV company, StarTimes, have called for more support to be given to Nigerians living with the virus across the country. From L: Justin Zhang, Chief Executive Officer, StarTimes Nigeria; Abdul Dangirma,… [+1701 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(107, 'Amanda Kooser', 'NASA, SpaceX push back Crew Dragon test launch to ISS - CNET', 'We\'ll have to wait a few more days before Crew Dragon earns its space wings.', 'https://www.cnet.com/news/nasa-spacex-push-back-crew-dragon-test-launch-to-iss/', 'https://cnet2.cbsistatic.com/img/TWljLwD1Ji5B5cc5ktNkYtnKAiA=/724x407/2018/12/10/3ccb3693-841b-4f71-a59a-7d4005074a63/crewdragontestchamber.jpg', '2018-12-10T17:19:00Z', 'The SpaceX Crew Dragon during testing in an anechoic chamber earlier in 2018. Elon Musk The next big step forward for NASA\'s Commercial Crew Program has hit a slight delay. The first test launch of SpaceX\'s Crew Dragon capsule is now scheduled for Jan. 17. NA… [+1150 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(108, 'trentfitzgerald', 'Ty Dolla Sign Indicted on Felony Drug Possession Charges - XXLMAG.COM', 'A grand jury has indicted Ty Dolla Sign on drug charges that include felony possession of cocaine.', 'http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2018/12/ty-dolla-sign-indicted-felony-drug-possession-charges/', 'https://townsquare.media/site/812/files/2018/12/Ty-Dolla-Sign-Indicted-Drug-Charges.jpg?w=600&h=0&zc=1&s=0&a=t&q=89', '2018-12-10T17:06:00Z', 'Ty Dolla $ign has been indicted on three felony drug possession charges, including cocaine possession. According to TM, on Dec. 10, a grand jury indicted the \" Goin Thru Some Thangz \" rapper, born Tyrone Griffin Jr., on three counts: felony possession of coca… [+1177 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(109, 'Chris Morris', 'Apple\'s Problems in China May Have Just Gotten Worse - Fortune', 'A court decision regarding Qualcomm patents could halt the sale and import of many models of the iPhone.', 'http://fortune.com/2018/12/10/apple-iphone-ban-china/', 'https://fortunedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2018/12/gettyimages-955849148.jpg', '2018-12-10T16:57:20Z', 'The market share for Apple’s iPhone in China has been shrinking for a little while. But a court decision that could halt the sale and import of most models of the iPhone into the country might have a dramatic impact on the company’s bottom line. Qualcomm, in … [+1594 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(110, 'https://www.facebook.com/tijani.emmanuel1', 'Nigerian army has committed war crimes against humanity, says ICC - TheCable', 'The International Criminal Court (ICC) says Nigerian security forces (NSF), including the Nigerian army, have committed war crimes against humanity.', 'https://www.thecable.ng/nigerian-army-has-committed-war-crimes-against-humanity-says-icc', 'https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Fatou-Bensouda-ICC.jpg', '2018-12-10T16:23:00Z', 'The International Criminal Court (ICC) says Nigerian security forces (NSF) have committed war crimes against humanity. In a report sent to TheCable, the ICC said it has received “a total of 169 communications” from Nigeria and its assessment has shown that se… [+3097 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(111, 'View all posts by Emmanuel Okogba ?', 'NSF: 19 year old sends off Oshonaike in table tennis quarter-finals - Vanguard', 'It was an exhilarating moment at the Indoor Sports Hall of the Abuja National Stadium, venue of the table tennis event of the ongoing National Sports Festival (NSF) as 19-year-old Nimota Aregbesola beat former African champion, Funke Oshonaike in the', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/2018/12/nsf-19-year-old-sends-off-oshonaike-in-table-tennis-quarter-fina', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Oshonaike.jpg', '2018-12-10T16:07:20Z', 'It was an exhilarating moment at the Indoor Sports Hall of the Abuja National Stadium, venue of the table tennis event of the ongoing National Sports Festival (NSF) as 19-year-old Nimota Aregbesola beat former African champion, Funke Oshonaike in the quarter-… [+1002 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(112, 'View all posts by adekunle ?', '2019: It’s time to leave Buhari’s train, Bolaji Abdullahi counsels Nigerians - Vanguard', 'Ahead of the 2019 Presidential election, a former spokesperson of the All Progressives Congress, APC, Bolaji Abdullahi has called on Nigerians to jump out of the train of President Muhammadu Buhari saying the man presiding over the affairs of the nat', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/2018/12/2019-its-time-to-leave-buharis-train-bolaji-abdullahi-counsels-n', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Screen-Shot-2018-05-19-at-04.15.20-e1526700236244.png', '2018-12-10T16:02:00Z', '…North, tired of incompetence, poor performance – Afegbua By Dirisu Yakubu ABUJA – Ahead of the 2019 Presidential election, a former spokesperson of the All Progressives Congress, APC, Bolaji Abdullahi has called on Nigerians to jump out of the train of Presi… [+4106 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(113, 'Karen McVeigh', 'UN states agree historic global deal to manage refugee crisis - The Guardian', 'First international pact on mass movements of people reached between 164 nations, despite US-led objections', 'https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2018/dec/10/un-states-agree-historic-global-deal-to-m', 'https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/6d3f13bc0fd07489f19f96bfc4065b26ea33264c/0_64_4568_2742/master/4568.jpg?width=1200&height=630&quality=85&auto=format&fit=crop&overlay-align=bottom%2Cleft&overlay-width=100p&overlay-base64=L2ltZy9zdGF0aWMvb3ZlcmxheXMvdGctZGVmYXVsdC5wbmc&s=756576f71d41ed99330a52472bf49995', '2018-12-10T15:58:00Z', 'The first ever international deal on the migration crisis was signed on Monday by a majority of UN states, despite vociferous objections led by the United States. The historic, non-binding global pact seeking to better manage mass migration was approved by de… [+3818 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(114, NULL, 'Enyimba rated high in Africa - FootballliveNG', 'Enyimba International Football Club have been placed at fifth position of the club-football rankings in the continent with 27 points, according to Africans Got Football. The People’s Elephants performed well at the 2018 CAF Confederation Cup before b', 'https://footballlive.ng/enyimba-rated-high-in-africa/', 'https://footballlive.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG-20181209-WA0014.jpg', '2018-12-10T15:47:00Z', 'Enyimba International Football Club have been placed at fifth position of the club-football rankings in the continent with 27 points, according to Africans Got Football. The People’s Elephants performed well at the 2018 CAF Confederation Cup before being bund… [+742 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(115, 'Mallory Locklear', 'NASA’s Voyager 2 probe has entered interstellar space - Engadget', 'It exited the heliosphere and crossed into interstellar space on November 5th.', 'https://www.engadget.com/2018/12/10/nasa-voyager-2-entered-interstellar-space/', 'https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?thumbnail=1200%2C630&quality=80&image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2018-12%252F2cfba370-fc8c-11e8-ae7e-d9de08f9d591%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3Dca707f8f8dc32a31bd06591805be733b09cec687&client=amp-blogside-v2&signature=d49c81aac86f88ef7b8a8accb7eeb62f8401cc98', '2018-12-10T15:34:47Z', '\"I think we\'re all happy and relieved that the Voyager probes have both operated long enough to make it past this milestone,\" Voyager Project Manager Suzanne Dodd said in a statement. \"This is what we\'ve all been waiting for. Now we\'re looking forward to what… [+2011 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(116, 'Jonathan Watts', 'Scientists identify vast underground ecosystem containing billions of micro-organisms - The Guardian', 'Global team of scientists find ecosystem below earth that is twice the size of world’s oceans', 'https://www.theguardian.com/science/2018/dec/10/tread-softly-because-you-tread-on-23bn-tonnes-of-mic', 'https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/6196dd70713adfe3aa105760d2873ea154c56f3e/411_45_3637_2182/master/3637.jpg?width=1200&height=630&quality=85&auto=format&fit=crop&overlay-align=bottom%2Cleft&overlay-width=100p&overlay-base64=L2ltZy9zdGF0aWMvb3ZlcmxheXMvdGctZGVmYXVsdC5wbmc&s=4649fe5c804e42240748abdaf75decf9', '2018-12-10T15:00:00Z', 'The Earth is far more alive than previously thought, according to deep life studies that reveal a rich ecosystem beneath our feet that is almost twice the size of that found in all the worlds oceans. Despite extreme heat, no light, minuscule nutrition and int… [+3722 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(117, 'View all posts by Emmanuel Okogba ?', 'Emir of Ilorin cautions Kwara gov’t against dragging him into politics.. - Vanguard', 'The Emir of Ilorin and Chairman Kwara State Traditional Council, Alhaji Ibrahim Sulu-Gambari, has cautioned kwara state government against dragging him into politics, describing himself as the father of all.', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/2018/12/emir-of-ilorin-cautions-kwara-state-govt-against-dragging-him-in', 'https://www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Ahmed1.jpg', '2018-12-10T14:57:00Z', 'By Demola Akinyemi Ilorin-The Emir of Ilorin and Chairman Kwara State Traditional Council, Alhaji Ibrahim Sulu-Gambari, has cautioned kwara state government against dragging him into politics, describing himself as the father of all. Governor Abdulfatah Ahmed… [+1712 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(118, 'https://www.facebook.com/tijani.emmanuel1', '‘We deserve the best’ — Abati asks Ogun people to vote Kashamu - TheCable', 'Reuben Abati, former senior special adviser to former president Goodluck Jonathan, says indigenes of Ogun state should vote for Buruji Kashamu.', 'https://www.thecable.ng/we-deserve-the-best-abati-asks-ogun-people-to-vote-kashamu', 'https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/ReubenAbati5.jpg', '2018-12-10T14:51:00Z', 'Reuben Abati, former senior special adviser to former president Goodluck Jonathan, says indigenes of Ogun state should vote for Buruji Kashamu, senator representing Ogun east. Speaking at the flag-off of the People Democratic Party (PDP) factional gubernatori… [+1515 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
