(120, 'Segun Otokiti', 'Comedian, on-air personality fight dirty over Pastor Adefarasin - WorldStage', 'WorldStage Newsonline--- Nigerian stand-up comedian Jephthah Bowoto, popularly known as Akpororo, has warned popular on-air personality Daddy Freeze to face him rather than attacking Pastor Paul Adefarasin.', 'https://www.worldstagegroup.com/comedian-on-air-personality-fight-dirty-over-pastor-adefarasin/', 'https://www.worldstagegroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Akpororo.jpg', '2018-12-10T14:23:00Z', 'WorldStage Newsonline— Nigerian stand-up comedian Jephthah Bowoto, popularly known as Akpororo, has warned popular on-air personality Daddy Freeze to face him rather than attacking Pastor Paul Adefarasin. The feud between the comedian and the founder of Free … [+1173 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(121, 'John Owen Nwachukwu', 'Electoral Act: Agbakoba fumes, tells Saraki, Dogara, what to do to President Buhari - Daily Post Nigeria', 'A senior lawyer, Olisa Agbakoba, has written the National Assembly, demanding that they override President Muhammadu Buhari on the Electoral Act Amendment', 'http://dailypost.ng/2018/12/10/electoral-act-agbakoba-fumes-tells-saraki-dogara-president-buhari/', 'http://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/saraki-dogara-tete-a-tete.jpg', '2018-12-10T13:45:46Z', 'A senior lawyer, Olisa Agbakoba, has written the National Assembly, demanding that they override President Muhammadu Buhari on the Electoral Act Amendment Bill. In a letter addressed to the Senate President, Dr Bukola Saraki and the Speaker of the House of Re… [+3588 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(122, NULL, 'BREAKING: Senate opens public hearing on vote-buying - The Punch', 'The Nigerian Senate has formally declared open the public hearing on vote-buying and improving electoral processes in the country.\r\n\r\nThis was contained in a tweet on the verified Twitter handle of...', 'https://punchng.com/breaking-senate-opens-public-hearing-on-vote-buying/', 'https://cdn.punchng.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/19122921/Senate1.jpg', '2018-12-10T12:46:00Z', 'The Nigerian Senate has formally declared open the public hearing on vote-buying and improving electoral processes in the country. This was contained in a tweet on the verified Twitter handle of the Nigerian Senate @ [email protected] Senate President, @bukol… [+7341 chars]', '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines'),
(123, 'Katrina Turrill', 'High blood pressure: Three foods containing hidden salt to cut down on - Express', 'HIGH blood pressure affects more than one in four adults in the UK, but many people may not realise they have it. Diet can have a huge impact on a person’s blood pressure reading - in particular, three foods should be avoided.', 'https://www.express.co.uk/life-style/health/1056740/high-blood-pressure-diet-foods-avoid-salt-bread-', 'https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/11/750x445/1056740.jpg', '2018-12-10T12:20:00Z', NULL, '2018/12/10 08:50:37pm', 'top-headlines');

